Text:
Excelente!!!! FULL :)

Video: 10/10
Audio: 10/10

Muchas gracias a eztv por compartir este gran trabajo y NO trabajar con archivos RARs.

;)

While I don't see the point of posting rar's on bittorrent since the purpose of rar's is to enable transfer of large files in pieces on usenet....I don't get the whining about such a trivial matter.  It's childishly simple to unarchive a set of rar files.   But anyway, props to eztv for upping such a fine show in peerless quality.
